title: Fifty Shades
alt: Wishbone and the Illustrated Classics series have gotten me through every conversation I've ever had about Dickens, Treasure Island, The Anarchist's Cookbook, and Our Bodies, Ourselves.
transcript:
As with most famous books, I've never actually read Fifty Shades of Grey.
I only know the plot from watching the Wishbone version.
